{"tid":136113,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人愈大愈來愈難識朋友 人性太得人驚..","createTime":"2017-02-26T21:18:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-27T06:47:15.000Z","uid":72212,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"91de958d22cf597154470563a9545929905da115","tid":136113,"uid":72212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T21:18:23.000Z","msg":"依個月見識到人性既一面<br />\n點解咁講?<br />\n分左手就關人撚事架啦<br />\n我琴日手賤wts左我前度 嘔到黃膽水出埋黎<br />\n佢都無理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為最後一次見佢果陣<br />\n佢同我講話關係唔同左<br />\n咁情侶關係先理 朋友唔洗理?<br />\n咁樣叫愛咩?到依加 我都好想親口聽佢講佢想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仆街黎 人總係犯賤<br />\n<br />\n另一方面 我真係唔識點識朋友<br />\n困係屋企 交友app多數呃錢呃蝦條 無個交心<br />\n出到去又好<br />\n啲人永遠見人講人話 見鬼講鬼話<br />\n變到依個世界好假<br />\n人既機心 自私 貪念 可以去到幾盡?<br />\n我諗大家總試過1.2次經驗...<br />\n<br />\n好想搵個結婚對象<br />\n好想識番啲朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講到依一刻 我都唔知自己做緊乜<br />\n純粹上黎叫春<br />\n<br />\n想知多啲可以睇我之前啲文<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/iambobo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fiambobo&d=oilSAI4QurnOyWEhgxZI0J4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=ae818676\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/iambobo</a>"},{"pid":"cb5602ab7a56acb13153875e1cf595c530750361","tid":136113,"uid":76117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T21:28:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7e52b4913523506146d1635aa2df1925bf0f7416","tid":136113,"uid":71826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T21:40:48.000Z","msg":"笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"136cbcff2576aec0087cfdd8fe1a356f28bc0a39","tid":136113,"uid":83941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T21:57:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6e5533d30b6176e8b7e38eadb1106ccad25ac96e","tid":136113,"uid":83941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T21:59:27.000Z","msg":"此回